      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。那参与者我放三个：DataFetcher、PandaScore API，还有Cache？Caller需要显示吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DataFetcher",
        "PandaScore",
        "Cache",
