        "Caller",
        "PandaScore API"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，参与者列好了。第一条消息是DataFetcher向Cache发起GET请求，key是team_history_123对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DataFetcher",
        "Cache",
        "GET team_history_123"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，然后要分两种情况：缓存命中直接返回数据；没命中就走else分支，DataFetcher去调PandaScore的/teams/123/matches接口，拿到JSON后解析，再写入缓存。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Cache Hit",
        "Cache Miss",
        "GET /teams/123/matches",
        "JSON response",
        "Parse matches",
        "SET team_history_123"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "写入缓存是DataFetcher自己完成的？不需要Cache返回确认吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DataFetcher",
        "Cache",
        "SET team_history_123"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，SET操作画成DataFetcher到Cache的虚线箭头就行，不用等返回。最后统一把match data返回给Caller。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DF-Cache SET",
        "DF--Caller Return match data"
